#show: lokta-report.with(
  title: "Stock and surface",
  subtitle: "A short report on the four papers.",
  org: "The Lokta Office",
  meta: ("Author": "The Office", "Date": "1 April 2026", "Status": "Draft"),
)

= Surfaces
Each stock re-points the semantic layer. Build against the semantic tokens and a
document inherits theming and AA at once.

#lk-note(title: "Note", accent: lk-aubergine)[
  Marigold is a ground, not a tint. Use it full bleed behind dark text.
]

= Roles
The text roles are primary, body, secondary, and muted. All clear AA on the page
surface of every stock.
